quests.desc: I hope you're ready to go into rooms and interact with objects, because you've just entered TextWorld! Here is how to play! First thing I need you to do is to head north. Then, try to take a trip west. With that over with, move south. After that, move west. And then, pick up the type 2 passkey from the table inside the sauna. Then, try to travel east. After that, make sure that the type 2 safe is unlocked. After that, ensure that the type 2 safe is open. Then, recover the passkey from the type 2 safe in the dish-pit. After that, Deposit the passkey into the chest to lock it. Alright, thanks!

objective: You are now playing a profound game of TextWorld! Here is how to play! First off, if it's not too much trouble, I need you to head north. After that, take a trip west. That done, head south. After that, make an effort to travel west. After that, take the type 2 passkey from the table within the sauna. Having taken the type 2 passkey, try to head east. Then, check that the type 2 safe in the dish-pit is unlocked with the type 2 passkey. And then, assure that the type 2 safe is ajar. And then, retrieve the passkey from the type 2 safe. Then, doublecheck that the chest is locked with the passkey. Once that's all handled, you can stop!
